author: Hank Green
description:
It just seems like the whole point is to show off how disfunctional everything is and I hope to god that that backfires, not just against the current administration, but against the entire system we have of government being a game where opposing sides increasingly just hate each other and so actually doing something together is seen as losing. I have ideas for which things

title: This Shutdown is Different
